<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 18:18:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>举重：女子81公斤级以上，中国李娜强势表现摘得第二枚金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-li-wins-womens-over-81kg-gold-2024-08-11/</link><description>中国选手李雯雯在周日举行的巴黎奥运会女子举重81公斤以上级比赛中凭借出色表现夺得第二枚奥运金牌。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 12:27:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-li-wins-womens-over-81kg-gold-2024-08-11/</guid></item><item><title>外交部长表示，中国支持伊朗捍卫安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-iran-defending-security-says-foreign-minister-2024-08-11/</link><description>据中国外交部的一份声明称，中国外交部长王毅周日在电话中告诉伊朗代理外长，中国支持伊朗捍卫其“主权、安全和民族尊严”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 11:21:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-iran-defending-security-says-foreign-minister-2024-08-11/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国空军的行动“非法”、“鲁莽”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-actions-china-air-force-illegal-reckless-2024-08-11/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周日谴责中国空军在两国声称拥有主权的南海海域的行动，称这些行动“不公正、非法和鲁莽”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 06:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-actions-china-air-force-illegal-reckless-2024-08-11/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与中国就南海问题进行贸易指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-condemns-china-air-force-dangerous-acts-south-china-sea-2024-08-10/</link><description>这是自2022年小费迪南德·马科斯总统就任以来菲律宾首次抱怨中国飞机的危险行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 09:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-condemns-china-air-force-dangerous-acts-south-china-sea-2024-08-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国火箭解体使1000多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</link><description>分析人士周五表示，中国的一枚火箭级本周在太空中解体，产生了 700 多块碎片，使地球轨道交通繁忙区域的 1000 多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险碰撞的风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:03:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行表示将增加国债交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-says-it-will-increase-treasury-bond-trading-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国央行周五发布的第二季度货币政策执行报告称，中国央行将努力“丰富”货币政策工具箱，并在公开市场操作中逐步增加国债买卖。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 18:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-says-it-will-increase-treasury-bond-trading-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高管表示调查仍在继续，相信其中国电动汽车措施符合世贸组织</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-executive-confident-its-chinese-ev-measures-comply-with-wto-says-probe-2024-08-09/</link><description>欧盟执行机构周五表示，欧盟委员会相信其对中国电动汽车国家补贴的调查和针对中国电动汽车补贴的措施符合世界贸易组织的规则，并将继续进行调查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 15:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-executive-confident-its-chinese-ev-measures-comply-with-wto-says-probe-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人要求投资者加入重组程序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国恒大在周五提交的文件中表示，其清算人已邀请有兴趣重组这家负债累累的房地产开发商或其任何部分的投资者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与越南举行首次海岸警卫队联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</link><description>周五，菲律宾和越南船只的船员用水炮轰击一艘船只，并模拟搜救，这是两国海岸警卫队在南海与北京对峙的首次联合演习。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部称欧盟电动汽车初裁违反世贸组织规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国商务部周五表示，欧盟对进口电动汽车（EV）的初步裁决缺乏事实和法律依据，严重违反世界贸易组织（WTO）规则。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>斐济总理将于8月12日至21日访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，斐济总理西蒂维尼·拉布卡将于周一至8月21日访问中国，欢迎两国有机会建立战略关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 08:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份银行贷款将下降，北京将重点关注政策支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</link><description>周五路透调查显示，尽管央行加大了对经济的政策支持力度，但受信贷需求不温不火和季节性因素拖累，中国7月份新增人民币贷款可能较上月大幅下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着国内航空公司向海外扩张，外国航空公司对中国失去了兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</link><description>由于俄罗斯广阔空域飞往欧洲和北美的北方航线较短，中国航空公司享有成本优势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:56:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求一些券商对债券交易进行合规检查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国证券监管机构已下令一些券商检查其债券交易活动，当局试图遏制对中国政府债券的疯狂购买。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份降雨和洪水导致自然灾害损失近一倍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</link><description>这是自 2021 年以来 7 月份的最大损失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>